McWane

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


McWane, Inc.





Type

Private


Industry
Manufacturing


Founded
1921


Headquarters
Birmingham, Alabama, U.S.



Key people

C. Phillip McWane, Chairman
G. Ruffner Page, President


Products
Pipes, fittings, compressed air tanks, fire extinguishers


Revenue
$1.7 billion USD (2014)



