Executive Profile
Charles Phillip McWane  Independent Director, National Commerce CorporationAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 4 Board Members in 4 different organizations across 4 different industries.See Board Relationships59$30,600
Background

		Mr. Charles Phillip McWane served as the President of Mcwane, Inc. from 1995 to 1998. Mr. McWane served as an Executive Vice President of Mcwane, Inc. He joined Mcwane, Inc. in 1980. He has been the Chairman of Mcwane, Inc. since 1999. He serves as a Vice Chairman of The Children's Hospital Of Alabama. He has been an Independent Director at National Commerce Corporation since 2010. He has been a Director of Mcwane, Inc. since 1986. He serves as a Director of the National ... Bank of Commerce and First American Bank. He served as Director of Alabama National Bancorporation since 1995. He is a Member of the Rotary Club of Birmingham and serves on the Boards of Sloss Furnaces Foundation, The McWane Center Endowment Fund and The Children's Hospital of Alabama Finance Committee. Mr. McWane graduated in 1980 from Auburn University in Auburn, Alabama with a Degree in Business and Industrial Management.Read Full Background




