McWane | Corporate Homepage














































Best in the Business
McWane is proud to manufacture premium products for customers around the world. When it comes to water infrastructure, technology solutions and support, we’re the industry leader.









A Culture of Accountability
Excellence of health and safety performance are vital parts of the culture that McWane has worked so hard to build and sustain. For generations, the word “quality” has been synonymous with McWane.
Learn More 









Good Neighbors
Our family of companies is committed to supporting local communities. In small towns and big cities, we’re giving back to the people that live, work and buy from McWane.
Learn More 









Why Buy American?
Understanding the "Buy America" Requirements for Water Infrastructure Projects
Learn More 











For Generations
At the McWane Family of Companies, we cast ductile iron products — including pipe, valves, hydrants, fittings, and plumbing products — manufacture fire extinguishers, fire suppression systems, steel pressure vessels, and build network switches and monitoring equipment.
We continue to be the leader in delivering clean, safe drinking water around the world.







McWane Environmental Focus






Protecting the Environment for Generations to Come
Each year McWane recycles over 750,000 tons of scrap iron. Our products are reliable, durable and sustainable for generations.
Learn about our commitment





